snippet.title: Elementyle Alpha Trailer - Now Available on Steam
snippet.description:
Elementyle, a free-to-play chess-like strategy game is coming to Steam on July 31st, 2024!

Audio is licensed through TakeTones - Flight of the Mind

Steam Page Now Live! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3056310/Elementyle/
